- .NET Framework 4 and 4.5
- Windows Store apps
- Windows Phone 8 and 8.1
- Portable Class Libraries
More documentation on the API is available at: https://developers.google.com/api-client-library/dotnet/apis/pubsub/v1beta1a
The package source code is available at: https://developers.google.com/resources/api-libraries/download/pubsub/v1beta1a/csharp
